<li id="cite_note-32"><b><a href="#cite_ref-32" title="">^</a></b> David Fontana (2005): Is there an afterlife. A comprehensive overview of the evidence.</li>
<li id="cite_note-33"><b><a href="#cite_ref-33" title="">^</a></b> Fontana (2005), p. 324-51. See also www.thescoleexperiment.com</li>
