<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Buddhism" title="Buddhism">Buddhism</a> (<a href="/wiki/Naraka_(Buddhism)" title="Naraka (Buddhism)">Naraka</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Chinese_mythology" title="Chinese mythology">Chinese mythology</a> (<a href="/wiki/Diyu" title="Diyu">Diyu</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Christianity" title="Christianity">Christianity</a> (<a href="/wiki/Limbo" title="Limbo">Limbo</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hell_in_Christian_beliefs" title="Hell in Christian beliefs">Hell</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ancient_Egyptian_religion" title="Ancient Egyptian religion">Ancient Egyptian religion</a> (<a href="/wiki/Duat" title="Duat">Duat</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Germanic_paganism" title="Germanic paganism">Germanic</a> and <a href="/wiki/Death_in_Norse_paganism" title="Death in Norse paganism">Norse paganism</a> (<a href="/wiki/Hel_(location)" title="Hel (location)">Hel</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Niflheim" title="Niflheim">Niflheim</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Greek_mythology" title="Greek mythology">Greek mythology</a> (<a href="/wiki/Hades" title="Hades">Hades</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tartarus" title="Tartarus">Tartarus</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hinduism" title="Hinduism">Hinduism</a> (<a href="/wiki/Naraka" title="Naraka">Naraka</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Islam" title="Islam">Islam</a> (<a href="/wiki/Jahannam" title="Jahannam">Jahannam</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Judaism" title="Judaism">Judaism</a> (<a href="/wiki/Gehennom" title="Gehennom" class="mw-redirect">Gehennom</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sheol" title="Sheol">Sheol</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Shinto" title="Shinto">Shinto</a> (<a href="/wiki/Yomi" title="Yomi">Yomi</a>)</span></p>
